org.apache.oodt.cas.resource.jobqueue

Interface JobQueue

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JobStack

    public interface JobQueue
    Version:
    $Revision$

    An interface for persisting JobSpecs used by a JobQueueController.

    .
    Author:
    mattmann
